---
// About tab: bio (left) + self-as-a-dataset terminal cards (right).
---

<div class="about">
  <div class="about__main">
    <img
      class="about__avatar"
      src="/avatar.jpg"
      width="112"
      height="112"
      alt="Stanley Tejakusuma avatar"
      loading="lazy"
      decoding="async"
    />
    <div class="about__bio">
      <p>
        Hey hey! I'm Stanley. I live and breathe data, working between the blockchain and analytics
        space. Started out as a data scientist and it became a habit I can't shake: markets,
        blockchains, models, even my own routines all look like datasets to me. Sometimes I break
        things along the way, but that's part of the learning curve 😉.
      </p>
      <p>
        I rarely stop at the analysis. I build the pipelines that collect the data, the models that
        learn from it, and the tools that act upon it — and I care a ton about making them simple
        enough to actually trust.
      </p>
      <p>
        Off the clock: a Tennis or Padel court, or the nearest mountain in Java. Stay hungry, stay
        foolish.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about__side">
    <div class="tcard">
      <p class="tcard__cmd"><span class="tcard__prompt">visitor@stanley:~$</span> cat stanley.json</p>
      <pre class="tcard__out">{`{`}
  <span class="k">"base"</span>: <span class="v">"Jakarta · UTC+7"</span>,
  <span class="k">"alma_mater"</span>: <span class="v">"Purdue '24 — data science"</span>,
  <span class="k">"daily_drivers"</span>: [<span class="v">"python"</span>, <span class="v">"sql"</span>, <span class="v">"dbt"</span>, <span class="v">"typescript"</span>],
  <span class="k">"obsessions"</span>: [<span class="v">"on-chain data"</span>, <span class="v">"llms"</span>, <span class="v">"market microstructure"</span>],
  <span class="k">"first_job"</span>: <span class="v">"starbucks barista ☕"</span>,
  <span class="k">"motto"</span>: <span class="v">"stay hungry, stay foolish"</span>
{`}`}</pre>
    </div>

    <div class="tcard">
      <p class="tcard__cmd"><span class="tcard__prompt">visitor@stanley:~$</span> ./time_allocation --weekly</p>
      <pre class="tcard__out">chasing_signals  <span class="bar">▓▓▓▓▓▓▓▓</span><span class="dim">░░</span>
building_tools   <span class="bar">▓▓▓▓▓▓▓</span><span class="dim">░░░</span>
backtesting      <span class="bar">▓▓▓▓▓</span><span class="dim">░░░░░</span>
tennis_padel     <span class="bar">▓▓▓</span><span class="dim">░░░░░░░</span>
mountain_air     <span class="bar">▓▓</span><span class="dim">░░░░░░░░</span>
<span class="dim">// error bars omitted. n=1, results may not replicate.</span></pre>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .about {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 0.92fr);
    gap: clamp(1.5rem, 3.5vw, 3rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .about__avatar {
    float: left;
    width: clamp(72px, 8vw, 88px);
    height: auto;
    margin: 0.2rem 1.25rem 0.6rem 0;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 12px;
  }

  .about__bio {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.86rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-fg) 72%, var(--color-muted));
  }

  .about__bio p {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .about__bio p + p {
    margin-top: 0.85rem;
  }

  .about__side {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .tcard {
    padding: 0.9rem 1.05rem 1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-surface) 55%, transparent);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .tcard__cmd {
    margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
    color: var(--color-fg);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }

  .tcard__prompt {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .tcard__out {
    margin: 0;
    overflow-x: auto;
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-fg) 68%, var(--color-muted));
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .tcard__out .k {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .tcard__out .v {
    color: color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-fg) 85%, var(--color-muted));
  }

  .tcard__out .bar {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .tcard__out .dim {
    color: var(--color-muted);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  @media (max-width: 880px) {
    .about {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .about__avatar {
      float: none;
      display: block;
      margin: 0 0 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
